This paper discusses a new blockchain solution that addresses limitations to privacy, faithful execution, and transaction finality. It also focuses on reducing transaction latency and improving interoperability. Based on this, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DLT (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.SE (Software Engineering), and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
